            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced onion</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 8-10 min or until softened and caramelised</p><p>Once caramelised, add the<strong> sliced garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1641914349292-x200.jpg",
