      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the fat from your<strong> pork loin steaks </strong>and season each steak with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Lay the <strong>sage leaves </strong>on top of each steak then drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1641914386074-x200.jpg",
