    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes and parsnips have had 15 min, add the <strong>seasoned</strong> <strong>pork steaks</strong> and any extra <strong>sage leaves</strong> to the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a final 13-15 min or until the pork steaks are cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>sage-roasted pork steaks</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
